4.body: Before merging a Pull Request - check if documentaiton is up to date. Ideas: Docs Page automatically update if related project pushes to mainbranch. Project GitHub pages can be used for "development-stage" of docs (Gitub Action Deploys dev branch on update). Each project lead invites for contribution with an "how to" video.
